sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor UserA as Person A (Host)
    participant UIA as Frontend (Person A)
    participant REST as REST API Gateway
    participant WS as WebSocket Server
    participant UIB as Frontend (Person B)
    actor UserB as Person B (Guest)

    %% Flow 1: Person A starts the session
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
    Note over UserA, WS: 1. Live Session Creation
    UserA->>UIA: Clicks "Start Live Session"
    UIA->>REST: POST /sessions (Sends language selection)
    REST-->>UIA: Returns sessionId & websocketUrl
    UIA->>WS: Opens WebSocket (without token in URL)
    WS-->>UIA: Connection Open
    UIA->>REST: POST /auth/token (session-bound token)
    REST-->>UIA: Returns short-lived runtime token
    UIA->>WS: JSON AUTH {token}
    WS-->>UIA: AUTH_STATUS (AUTHORIZED)
    UIA->>UserA: Requests Microphone access
    UIA->>UIA: Shows "Copy Invitation Link"
    end

    %% Flow 2: Person B joins via link
    rect rgb(245, 255, 250)
    Note over UserA, UserB: 2. Invitation and Connection
    UserA->>UserB: Sends link (ex: /?join=sess_123)
    UserB->>UIB: Opens link in browser
    UIB->>UIB: JS detects ?join parameter
    UIB->>REST: POST /sessions/sess_123/join
    REST-->>UIB: Returns websocketUrl
    UIB->>WS: Opens WebSocket (without token in URL)
    WS-->>UIB: Connection Open
    UIB->>REST: POST /auth/token (session-bound token)
    REST-->>UIB: Returns short-lived runtime token
    UIB->>WS: JSON AUTH {token}
    WS-->>UIB: AUTH_STATUS (AUTHORIZED)
    UIB->>UserB: Requests Microphone access
    end

    %% Flow 3: Real-time streaming and translation
    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
    Note over UserA, UserB: 3. Real-time Audio & Transcription
    
    %% Person A speaking
    UserA->>UIA: Speaks into microphone
    loop Every 250ms
        UIA->>WS: Sends Audio Chunk (Binary WebM)
    end
    
    %% Backend processing
    Note over WS: Backend (Kafka) performs VAD -> ASR -> MT -> TTS
    
    %% Sends transcript (Partial)
    WS-->>UIA: JSON: TRANSCRIPT_UPDATE (isFinal: false)
    WS-->>UIB: JSON: TRANSCRIPT_UPDATE (isFinal: false)
    UIA->>UserA: Shows grayed text (Listening...)
    UIB->>UserB: Shows grayed text (Translating...)

    %% Sends transcript (Final) + Audio
    WS-->>UIA: JSON: TRANSCRIPT_UPDATE (isFinal: true)
    WS-->>UIB: JSON: TRANSCRIPT_UPDATE (isFinal: true)
    UIA->>UserA: Finalizes speech bubble
    UIB->>UserB: Finalizes speech bubble
    
    %% Receives translated audio (Person B receives synthetic audio)
    WS-->>UIB: Binary data (Synthesized TTS Audio)
    UIB->>UserB: Plays translated audio
    end